erenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"모카","body":"숙제? 당연히 끝냈죠~\n난 우등생이니까~\n어떻게 봐도 「우등생!」라는 느낌이 뿜어져 나오죠?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"memorial168-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"모카","body":"잠깐만요, 그냥 넘기지 마세요~\n너무하네~","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"memorial168-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"모카","body":"숙제라고 하니까, 저번에 히~짱이 학교에\n참고서를 놓고 오는 바람에","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"memorial168-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"모카","body":"밤에 학교에 잠입해서 애들이랑 찾으러 갔는데요~……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"memorial168-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"모카","body":"「잠입하다」라는 말을 아무렇지도 않게 한다고요?\n뭐~ 이건 비밀이야기인 거로.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"memorial168-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"모카","body":"저희도 사실 그러고 싶지 않았다니까요?\n근데 히~짱이 「그 참고서가 없으면 숙제를 할 수 없어~!」\n……라고 하니까.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"memorial168-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"모카","body":"빵을 쏜다고 약속해서\n히~짱을 따라가기로 한 거예요.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"memorial168-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"모카","body":"참고서는 바로 찾았는데요,\n학교 출입문이 잠겨버려서……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"memorial168-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"모카","body":"우리는 갇혀버린 거예요. 야밤에, 학교에!\